channel.title: Links to new tunes we create
channel.description:
Hello everyone,
Thought we could post links to new tunes we create in here. That way we'll all know when you post something new on soundcloud or otherwise. Here's my latest. Look forward to hearing yours!
https://soundcloud.com/semper-sonics/skyline
